Your version is already clear and well-written! Here’s a slightly refined version to make the tone more natural and polished for email communication:


---

Subject: Clarification on Macro Output and Data Verification

Hello [Recipient’s Name],
Good day!

I reviewed the macro and observed that when I run the RunAllMacros() subroutine, the output from MacroE() overlaps with the values generated by MacroC() and MacroD().

To proceed with verifying the condition of the 1st Vessel Column and 2nd Vessel Column, I’d like to confirm the actual data for the Booking Number and Control Number, as the other data fields appear to be blank.

If it’s convenient, may I schedule a short meeting to discuss this further at your preferred time and location?

Thank you and best regards,
[Your Name]


