Best regards,
[Your Name]


---

Option 2 – Slightly more formal

Hello [Recipient’s Name],
Good day!

Thank you for providing the available schedules. I’m fine with any of the listed time slots on Wednesday. Please feel free to select the one that best fits your schedule.

Kind regards,
[Your Name]


---

Option 3 – Friendly and concise

Hello [Recipient’s Name],

Thank you! Any of the given time slots on Wednesday would be fine with me. Please choose whichever works best for you.

Best,
[Your Name]


